data.description: This charming house on a corner lot is a must see. With quick and easy access to all major metro highways and Will Rogers Airport only minutes away, this location can't be beat. Three bedrooms and one and half baths. Large Kitchen and bathrooms have been completely renovated. Kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. 5 burner stainless steel gas stove and stainless steel dishwasher are included. Large living room with brand new carpet. There is also a 10x10 cellar with indoor access. Perfect as a storm shelter as well as storage. There is also a second living space just off the living room and kitchen that could serve as a large dining room or a den. Home is equipped with a whole house water softener system. No hard water here! Brand new HVAC system installed in July 2023. Some windows have been updated already and a brand new French door installed in August 2023. Backyard has a small shed and two large decks. Home also has 2 driveways for plenty of parking. Agent is related to seller.
